data.title: "Chef's Table" Enrique Olvera (TV Episode 2016)
data.meta_description: Enrique Olvera: Directed by Clay Jeter. With Colman Andrews, Daniel Humm, Enrique Olvera. At the forefront of transforming Mexican cuisine, Enrique Olvera champions traditional ingredients under a haute perspective as he delves into the roots of Mexico to create award-winning dishes at his restaurant, Pujol.
